Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:06.84,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}I just feel my shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:09.99,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}空に　rise & ride
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:24.57,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be1}じれったい夢だって　最初からわかってた
