Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 為了增進我們的友誼要？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露營！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:42.98,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,480)}生存戰爭！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OVA第二話 生存戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教官熱心幫我們租借到了這塊露營地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 一定要好好拿出成果來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡被我們全包了 一般人禁止入內
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也不用擔心被人偷看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 那麼接下來大家要？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子跳下去很危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯哦 如果不好好做一下準備運動的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~腳抽筋啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救她們嘍~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就去救！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來救妳們了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 用力往上拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力拉~用力拉~用力拉~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺氣氛好像很熱烈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒啦 都得救啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲~萬歲~萬歲~萬歲~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們來設置帳篷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次嘗試 感覺好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒試過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 都包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是宿營地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿營地是指什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是露營場的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶~吶吶~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 為什麼大家都換上泳衣了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想啊 大家都穿泳衣只有我們沒換很奇怪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿泳衣才奇怪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好睏..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子時間還太早了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睡就睡在帳篷裏面而不是上面啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 麻子學姐請不要睡覺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:02:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗希也不要有樣學樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看起來好像很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 等下我會負責把帳篷搭好的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來幫忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用一塊德式雨披就能作為帳篷來使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:14.10,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(522,660)}Zeltbahn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裡我們還是先把四塊連在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這些扣子把雨披連在一起 妳看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帳篷原來是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大開眼界了呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個是特殊的帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也帶來了能簡單組裝起來的帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 已經搭好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可愛~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚嗚..難得人家想體驗一下二戰的感覺說..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的帳篷固然不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過設置起來比較麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且住起來也不是很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以用這邊的如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這樣沒錯啦..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那邊好像更麻煩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！正確的擺法是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 我要幫忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想試試看！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡半途而廢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都做到一半了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就堅持到最後吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺舊舊的也蠻有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 難得這麼好的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就兩種都搭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有個異空間耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們在幹什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得應該沒什麼特別的含義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為華學姐是個更可靠的人耶..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 妳說的也沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 看起來都搭好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭得很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的準備體操也終於做完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長的準備體操一直做到現在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出乎意料地認真仔細呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說她還在做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始玩水 一起勒個去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起勒個去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起勒個去是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感覺好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一起勒個去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起勒個去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起勒個去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃桃也在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說沒笑就是沒笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做咖喱還是燒烤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到露營當然是燒烤啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 雖然煮一大鍋咖喱或濃湯確實很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那些食物無論在哪裡都能吃到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與之相比 燒烤不在這種室外的話享受不到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想沒那回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒烤的話在店裏也能吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,shut up！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長說燒烤就是燒烤！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就做燒烤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這麼決定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘鏘~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘鏘嘎鏘鏘鏘~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優花里學姐..這些是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的珍貴收藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各國給養！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:24.59,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,660)}ration
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優花里！剛才已經說了要做燒烤了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我說 ration是什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有個詞叫什麼摸擬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯 摸了個你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是模擬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.31,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,660)}simulation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不同嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一處是相同的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給養也可稱為戰鬥食品或者野戰糧食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指在軍事行動中吃的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也就是指軍糧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 就是午餐肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖繩風苦瓜炒豆腐裏加的那種肉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有做成握壽司來吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋+嗶！
